precis:
Order (a) determining that an aggregate of 180 days of honourable service
at CANADIAN FORCES STATION (CFS) ALERT since it began its operation on
September 1, 1958, is "SPECIAL SERVICE" within the meaning of the Special
Service Medal Regulations, and (b) revoking the previous determination
(Order in Council P.C. 1992-2435).
